functions.label: useInstallEntityStoreV2
description: Hook to install Entity Store V2. Should be called from the root Security Solution app component.

children.label: services
description: - Kibana services required to install Entity Store V2

children.label: requiresOneOf
description:
At least one must be present for identity to be valid.
This can be used to filter documents before the entity ID is calculated.

children.label: identitySourceFields
description:
All field names used in EUID composition, deduplicated
This can be used to extract the ID fields from the document.
